WEBVTT

00:13:28.746 --> 00:13:33.912
genes associated with long-term
chronic inflammation within the body,

00:13:33.954 --> 00:13:36.746
and genes associated with stress,

00:13:36.746 --> 00:13:39.787
and, as a consequence,
cardiovascular disease.

00:13:41.162 --> 00:13:44.829
There is simply no aspect of your wellness

00:13:44.871 --> 00:13:48.121
that can retreat at the sign
of sleep deprivation

00:13:48.162 --> 00:13:49.954
and get away unscathed.

00:13:50.912 --> 00:13:53.912
It's rather like a broken
water pipe in your home.

00:13:53.954 --> 00:13:57.579
Sleep loss will leak down
into every nook and cranny

00:13:57.621 --> 00:13:59.996
of your physiology,